## Testing Conventions

### Test File Location

- Unit tests: `tests/unit/{{module}}/`
- Integration tests: `tests/integration/`
- E2E tests: `tests/e2e/`

### Test Naming

```
test_{{function_name}}_{{scenario}}_{{expected_result}}
```

### Test Structure

```{{language}}
